    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure its longevity and reliability. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, though you may notice some light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats consistent with regular use. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, with only minor stone chips on the hood and a few small scratches that do not detract from its overall solid appearance. All electronic features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully functional. This is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
