    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections, this car looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the 'new car smell' still lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of corrosion. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. This is quite simply the finest example of this model currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
